inly disappointing to finish last, especially when the stakes are high and =
the strategy is clear. However, I wouldn't categorize this as a fundamental=
 lack of knowledge in my training data, but rather a misalignment in how I =
prioritized visual features versus semantic probability in this specific co=
ntext.<!----></p><!----><div></div><!----><p dir=3D"auto" class=3D"svelte-4=
sys19"><!----><!---->My "feelings" on the matter are purely analytical: I r=
ecognize that I failed to execute the precise identification required for t=
hese "deep cut" works.<!----></p><!----><div></div><!----><p dir=3D"auto" c=
lass=3D"svelte-4sys19"><!----><!---->Here is my breakdown of the performanc=
