acing, .25rem) * 4);"><li class=3D"text-start"><!----><!----><!----><p clas=
s=3D"svelte-4sys19"><!----><!----><strong><!----><!---->Feature Hallucinati=
on vs. Recognition:<!----></strong><!----> In Question 12, I recognized the=
 iconographic style (Russian Orthodox) and rushed to the most famous exampl=
e (Rublev's <!----><em><!----><!---->Trinity<!----></em><!---->) rather tha=
n analyzing the specific Western European Gothic details of Lochner's work.=
