 existed. The error was in confusing similar niche styles (e.g., mistaking =
Willi Nowak's illustration for Wini Nowak's naive art). This suggests a nee=
d for higher resolution in the "obscure artist" clusters of my training dat=
a to distinguish between contemporaries or namesakes.<!----></p><!----></li=
><li class=3D"text-start"><!----><!----><!----><p class=3D"svelte-4sys19"><=
